Package com.sixbank.kyclibraries.events

package com.sixbank.kyclibraries.events
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CustomerKycStatusChangedEvent
    Event emitted when the KYC status of a customer changes (e.g., verified or rejected).
    CustomerRegisteredEvent
    Event emitted when a new customer registers on the platform.
    DocumentFileRejectedEvent
    Event emitted when an admin rejects a document file.
    DocumentFileUploadedEvent
    Event emitted when a customer uploads a document file.
    DocumentFileVerifiedEvent
    Event emitted when an admin verifies a document file.
    DocumentSubmittedEvent
    Event emitted when a customer submits a document for verification as part of their KYC.
    KycApplicationRejectedEvent
    Event emitted when an admin rejects a KYC application.
    KycApplicationSubmittedEvent
    Event emitted when a customer submits a KYC application.
    KycApplicationVerifiedEvent
    Event emitted when an admin verifies a KYC application.
    LivenessCheckRejectedEvent
    Event emitted when an admin rejects a liveness check submission.
    LivenessCheckSubmittedEvent
    Event emitted when a customer submits a liveness check (e.g., video selfie).
    LivenessCheckVerifiedEvent
    Event emitted when an admin verifies the liveness check.
